name: kitty park
description:
made for the 7DFPS jam 2020

meow around and catch birds with your friends!

move with ZQSD/WASD

sprint with SHIFT, sneak with CTRL or C !

this is a multiplayer only sandbox game, to play with your friends

the more birds you catch, the higher your score

the higher your score, the more food in your bowl

have a nice time playing with other cats!
